  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destinata FULL RED Edition is the finally long waited version of Destinata Red, implosioning from <strong><i>\"colors\"!</i></strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/091aa2d142d568575f494cf8192e1a74.poster.avif?t=1705098502\" width=332 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/091aa2d142d568575f494cf8192e1a74.webm?t=1705098502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/091aa2d142d568575f494cf8192e1a74.mp4?t=1705098502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The moon is falling, its shredded pieces are approaching menacingly towards us and there is only one path towards, Take down the enemy targets, and fight them until death.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/bafd25d6737aa25780a49d9252edbb98.poster.avif?t=1705098502\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/bafd25d6737aa25780a49d9252edbb98.webm?t=1705098502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/bafd25d6737aa25780a49d9252edbb98.mp4?t=1705098502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Destinata Full Red edition contains:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>cute Pixel Art and Characters!<br><br></strong></li><li>Hand made animations and unique <strong><i>2d indie pixel art metroidvania</i></strong> art stlye!<br><br></li><li>Different branches and elections throughout the game!<br><br></li><li>Hand drew HD full 4k images (sometimes pixeled due to system necessities)!<br><br></li><li><i>A false and grotesque sensation of thinking about a future with happiness that will never be reached not matter any decision, constrained by destiny we will not escape.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2></i></li><li>weird People!</li></ul></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And Most Importantly..........</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/f8b466e33f25cdb52bd9fdf803b4a952.poster.avif?t=1705098502\" width=526 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/f8b466e33f25cdb52bd9fdf803b4a952.webm?t=1705098502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/f8b466e33f25cdb52bd9fdf803b4a952.mp4?t=1705098502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
