m necessities)!<br><br></li><li><i>A false and grotesque sensation of thinking about a future with happiness that will never be reached not matter any decision, constrained by destiny we will not escape.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2></i></li><li>weird People!</li></ul></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And Most Importantly..........</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/f8b466e33f25cdb52bd9fdf803b4a952.poster.avif?t=1705098502\" width=526 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/f8b466e33f25cdb52bd9fdf803b4a952.webm?t=1705098502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489160/extras/f8b466e33f25cdb52bd9fdf803b4a952.mp4?t=1705098502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
